<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM4.9">
<l>ceṭiyāya valviṉaikaḷ tīrkkun tirumālē</l>
<l>neṭiyāṉē vēṅkaṭavā niṉkōyi liṉvācal</l>
<l>aṭiyārum vāṉavaru marampaiyaruṅ kiṭantiyaṅkum</l>
<l>paṭiyāyk kiṭantuṉ pavaḷavāy kāṇpēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Tirumāl who destroys forceful karmas that are evil!</l>
<l>O tall One! O You of Veṅkaṭa!</l>
<l>At the entrance of Your temple,</l>
<l rend="indent">I shall see Your red coral lips,</l>
<l rend="indent">lying as a step,</l>
<l rend="indent">on which devotees, celestial beings, Rambhā and the like dwell [and] walk about.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
